{"id": "QmZqngt1jBSYQ8NX8eabWAP5t1NiZcDJaFMfi56CDcSmjf", "title": "Should we have a way to automatically adjust prices based on exchange rate?", "body": "> by 0x739eb7914cd124d049d999c6f1874914af4f5337 (SinKillerJ#5337)\n\nWith the recent spike in the exchange rate of MANA many reasonably priced items are now absurd. Rather than having to manually adjust these prices, what if a seller could simply say \"always target the equivalent of $5 USD\". Obviously this would be an opt-in system as not everyone would want to, but it would help prevent this situation from happening again.\n\n- Yes\n- No\n- Invalid question/options\n\n\n**[Vote on this proposal on the Decentraland DAO](https://governance.decentraland.org/proposal/?id=a3d8a710-3a67-11ec-be0c-afec86cba5e5)**", "choices": ["Yes", "No", "Invalid question/options"], "start": 1635697680, "end": 1636302480, "snapshot": "13525875", "state": "closed", "author": "0x5E23D08324f017d5425e59A2782C9ae27aCE0958", "space": {"id": "snapshot.dcl.eth", "name": "Decentraland"}, "votes": 9, "votes_data": [{"id": "QmS8U3zxEsTgaV5TDep7KLYAHAjZpAAARh8Yjx26bDztST", "voter": "0xa4244F6711052752E6Bb0271Bf17c756E6598406", "created": 1636071362, "choice": 2, "space": {"id": "snapshot.dcl.eth"}}, {"id": "QmTUVuY9G3kcDkAmxBwSyQapLbY9zgX7ysziexbb7apt39", "voter": "0x6cAa802c6895ECD31601518C7f6B9eF6f9349238", "created": 1636050227, "choice": 2, "space": {"id": "snapshot.dcl.eth"}}, {"id": "QmXKnd6LR7FH86k6GG1h4mWANv7g5L45DD5qrTgU5CDeDj", "voter": "0x47DCBdF671dC8808d1397bDA92B2cAA4a7c4e951", "created": 1635864889, "choice": 2, "space": {"id": "snapshot.dcl.eth"}}, {"id": "0x4235029a4724658f07ef89cbaaa6b53ed80121fcd449c995ba1cda7db40f072f", "voter": "0xea886349d44AA81DE644f0F02105707f563103E6", "created": 1635835333, "choice": 2, "space": {"id": "snapshot.dcl.eth"}}, {"id": "QmbPEuGZhEt7qEnD8DR3p7y3eXJSBKQs3eBhmz3oGy9jzC", "voter": "0x7AaAaE8cd46aB71E1e5084d55d9C6b3ea4D970a0", "created": 1635824038, "choice": 2, "space": {"id": "snapshot.dcl.eth"